WEBVTT

00:10:59.440 --> 00:11:01.967
the belief that the man
is the head of the household,

00:11:01.991 --> 00:11:04.230
that the wife's place is in the home

00:11:04.254 --> 00:11:05.407
and most important,

00:11:05.431 --> 00:11:08.562
honor thy husband,
and 'til death do us part.

00:11:08.586 --> 00:11:10.308
These are gone.

00:11:10.332 --> 00:11:12.881
They are going, and in many places,

00:11:12.905 --> 00:11:14.293
they are gone.

00:11:14.317 --> 00:11:17.740
We are right now in a marriage revolution.

00:11:17.764 --> 00:11:22.479
We are shedding 10,000 years
of our farming tradition

00:11:22.503 --> 00:11:28.129
and moving forward towards egalitarian
relationships between the sexes --

00:11:28.153 --> 00:11:32.968
something I regard as highly compatible
with the ancient human spirit.